  "remarks": "Drex Technologies is wholly owned by Rami Makhlouf, who is listed under Union sanctions for providing financial support to the former al-Assad regime. Rami Makhlouf uses Drex Technologies to facilitate and manage his international financial holdings, including a majority share in SyriaTel, which the Union has previously listed on the grounds that it also provides financial support to the former al-Assad regime.",
